cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning techniques and optimization, which are primarily covered under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also introduces a new learned model for image classification, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the importance of prior knowledge and engineering in deep learning, which is relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper presents results on a new benchmark problem, which is related to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
